{"tid":1617192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港Haagen-Dazs無良心商戶","createTime":"2019-10-03T16:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T20:30:36.000Z","uid":276502,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d34a9eee2de5dc9668c73535c45215f7d69f8827","tid":1617192,"uid":276502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"喺69前，買左張Haagen-Dazs coupon，9月30日到期。<br />\n<br />\n69 612 616 71 721 ... 811 ... 831 ... 928 929...點會有心情......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無人預計到抗爭持續4個月...政府無能！黑警濫暴！黨鐵擾民！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要用張coupon時：<br />\n一係就係你唔敢開舖(我要用，係你唔俾我甪，我責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n二就係CCTV影住個九龍黨鐵站落哂閘，岀哂防暴(你話係我選擇，有事我責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n三黨鐵封埋站，我打去店舖想確定開舖，就算務住生命危險都要用張coupon，但係你哋&rdquo;long&rdquo;起電話(又係我責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n四星期一工作天(死線日)，打去搵CS，只係得留言，我都留言講清楚我個情況同coupon到期日。最後，CS江小姐都要等到10月2日下午先覆，佢哋公司無任何安排。<br />\n<br />\n你哋咩責任都無㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋唔敢開舖，叫人體諒，你哋又有無體諒你嘅顧客呢？<br />\n<br />\n坦白講句，一張coupon值幾錢丫，點解我要花咁多時間打俾你哋？因為我好想知，貴公司點處理今時今日政治帶俾你哋嘅問題！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n答案係: 無安排！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實哩個答案唔岀奇，只要你哋試過同Haagen-Dazs CS江小姐溝通過，你哋就會明白。<br />\n<br />\n香港Haagen-Dazs，不了！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d606cf36849cc1a4e4aaf119628a62f241405b2","tid":1617192,"uid":143151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"其實佢係有良心 先落得早閘姐<br />\n咪乜都屌啦"},{"pid":"670dc0aa838c6f857ad2cdad8b566131e6c585be","tid":1617192,"uid":9793,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d34a9eee2de5dc9668c73535c45215f7d69f8827","tid":1617192,"uid":276502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"喺69前，買左張Haagen-Dazs coupon，9月30日到期。<br />\n<br />\n69 612 616 71 721 ... 811 ... 831 ... 928 929...點會有心情......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無人預計到抗爭持續4個月...政府無能！黑警濫暴！黨鐵擾民！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要用張coupon時：<br />\n一係就係你唔敢開舖(我要用，係你唔俾我甪，我責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n二就係CCTV影住個九龍黨鐵站落哂閘，岀哂防暴(你話係我選擇，有事我責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n三黨鐵封埋站，我打去店舖想確定開舖，就算務住生命危險都要用張coupon，但係你哋&rdquo;long&rdquo;起電話(又係我責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal